Abstract = {We consider a model, given by two interacting electrons in an external
   harmonic potential, that can be solved analytically for a discrete and
   infinite set of values of the spring constant. The knowledge of the
   exact electronic density allows us to construct the exact
   exchange-correlation potential; and exchange-correlation energy by
